name: click-plugins
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.1.1" %}

package:
  name: click-plugins
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/c/click-plugins/click-plugins-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 46ab999744a9d831159c3411bb0c79346d94a444df9a3a3742e9ed63645f264b

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - click >=3.0
  run:
    - python
    - click >=3.0

test:
  imports:
    - click_plugins

about:
  home: https://github.com/click-contrib/click-plugins
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'An extension module for click to enable registering CLI commands via setuptools entry-points'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
